<div class="scp-image-block block-right" style="width:300px;"><img src="http://scp-wiki.wdfiles.com/local--files/apas/dro-0001" style="width:300px;" alt="dro-0001" class="image" />
<div class="scp-image-caption" style="width:300px;">
<p>Site of primary DRO-0001 manifestations, taken prior to AL-908 developing antimemtic properties.</p>
